text:
  Vitalik Buterin's ETH Sell-Off 94% Complete   Only 905 ETH Remaining

Vitalik Buterin has sold 15,479 of a planned 16,384 ETH since February 2, totaling approximately $30.94 million at an average price of ~$1,999 per ETH. The remaining ~905 ETH are expected to be sold within the next 3-4 hours.

@Money

  Vitalik Buterin's Massive ETH Sell-Off Nears Completion

According to Onchain Lens data, Vitalik Buterin has sold approximately 15,479 ETH (~$30.94M) since February 2nd, completing about 94% of his planned 16,384 ETH disposal at an average price of ~$1,999. The remaining ~905 ETH is expected to be fully sold within the next 3-4 hours.

